                        </div> 
                        
                        <div class="inline-block">
                            <span class="green-text big-text"><span class="border-bottom">slǣpendne</span> </span><br>
                            <span class="green-text">Participle/Adjective</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="inline-block">
                            <span class="yellow-text big-text border-bottom">man</span><br>
